{"service_name": "Capgemini Information Security Management System (ISMS)", "service_id": "7459867706250099", "company_name": "Capgemini UK plc", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Capgemini UK plc\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Capgemini Information Security Management System (ISMS)\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Cap Gemini can provide cloud-based log management and analytics service that leverages machine-generated big data to deliver real-time IT insights using Sumo solution and services. This could enable the use of PCI dashboards and compliances solution for their digital applications.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Services delivered by ISO27001 qualified Lead Auditors.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides risk and gap analysis against  ISO27001:2013 standards.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Analysis of in-house and supplier delivered services.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Identification of applicable ISO27001 control objectives.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Performance evaluation and recommendations for Key Performance Indicators\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assess  compliance with controls and tests their effectiveness.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Appropriate and proportionate quality controls with effective record keeping.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Monitoring and support for treatment of recommendations raised.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Establishment of an Information Security Forum for business leaders.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Fully scalable solution, tailored to organisational needs.\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Aligns clients\u2019 security management to ISO27001:2013 in preparation for certification.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Establishes policies and objectives for information security management.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Implement controls to manage and mitigate risks to information security.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Establish an effective governance framework through regular management review.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Incorporates sustainable and repeatable practices and measures.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enables the establishment of a continuous security improvement culture.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Identify, manage and reduce risks to critical information assets.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Evaluates security controls, their effectiveness and implementation status.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assesses existing ISMS  coverage and effectiveness.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supports transition from ISO27001:2005, through gap analysis and recommendation.\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3276.00 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92224/7459867706250099-pricing-document-2015-10-06-0830.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://asset